PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FAn American journalist was kidnapped
OL,8,Fin Baghdad, Iraq, on Tuesday,
OL,9,Faccording to Iraqi officials.
OL,11,FThe freelance journalist has been
OL,12,Fnamed Shelly Kittleson by one of the
OL,13,Foutlets she worked for.
OL,15,FThe US government is tracking her
OL,16,Fkidnapping and working with officials
OL,17,Fin Iraq to secure her release, a US
OL,18,Fofficial has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FThe Iraqi ministry confirmed a foreign
OL,8,Fjournalist had been kidnapped but did
OL,9,Fnot provide any further details.
OL,11,FIt remains unclear who is responsible
OL,12,Ffor Ms Kittleson's abduction. However,
OL,13,Fa US official blamed the Iran-backed
OL,14,Fmilitia Kataib Hezbollah.
OL,16,FTwo Iraqi security officials, who
OL,17,Fspoke to the Associated Press on
OL,18,Fcondition of anonymity because they
OL,19,Fwere not authorised to speak publicly
OL,20,Fon the case, said the journalist was a
OL,21,Fwoman and a US citizen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FThey said that two cars were involved
OL,8,Fin the kidnapping. One of which
OL,9,Fcrashed while being pursued near the
OL,10,Ftown of Al-Haswa in Babil province,
OL,11,Fsouthwest of Baghdad.
OL,13,FThe journalist was then transferred to
OL,14,Fa second car, which fled the scene.
OL,16,FIraq's interior ministry said security
OL,17,Fforces had launched an operation to
OL,18,Ftrack down the kidnappers and
OL,19,Fintercepted a vehicle belonging to the
OL,20,Fkidnappers that overturned as they
OL,21,Ftried to flee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FOne suspect was arrested, and one of
OL,8,Fthe vehicles used in the kidnapping
OL,9,Fwas seized, but others remain on the
OL,10,Floose, the statement said.
OL,12,FKittleson's journalism specialises in
OL,13,Fthe Middle East and Afghanistan, with
OL,14,Fwork published in international, US,
OL,15,Fand Italian outlets.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FITV News' US partner CNN has reported
OL,8,Fthat sources have said that Ms
OL,9,FKittleson was warned of threats
OL,10,Fagainst her, including kidnapping,
OL,11,Ffrom Iranian proxy group Kataib
OL,12,FHezbollah.
OL,14,FAccording to one source familiar with
OL,15,Fthe warning, the US government
OL,16,Frecently warned Kittleson of a Kataib
OL,17,FHezbollah plot to kidnap or kill her.
OL,19,FThe warning came while she was already
OL,20,Freporting in Iraq.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FAnother source said that US and Iraqi
OL,8,Fofficials had been tracking threats by
OL,9,Fan Iranian proxy against Kittleson,
OL,10,Fincluding threats to abduct or kill
OL,11,Fher, and had warned her to leave
OL,12,Fmultiple times in recent weeks.
OL,14,FThe US Embassy in Baghdad declined to
OL,15,Fcomment when asked by the Associated
OL,16,FPress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FThe US State Department has issued a
OL,8,Fstatement, saying the Trump
OL,9,Fadministration "has no higher priority
OL,10,Fthan the safety and security of
OL,11,FAmericans" and that it is "tracking
OL,12,Fthese reports."
OL,14,FUS-based news organisation, Al-
OL,15,FMonitor, confirmed the abduction of Ms
OL,16,FKittleson, who works as a contributor
OL,17,Ffor the outlet.
OL,26,@qD@POUsD@JO]sD@[OUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FAl-Monitor said it was "deeply
OL,8,Falarmed" by the abduction of
OL,9,FKittleson, who works as a contributor
OL,10,Ffor the news outlet.
OL,12,F"We call for her safe and immediate
OL,13,Frelease. We stand by her vital
OL,14,Freporting from the region and call for
OL,15,Fher swift return to continue her
OL,16,Fimportant work," the statement added.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@HO]tD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FThe US Embassy in Iraq has repeatedly
OL,8,Fwarned US citizens to leave the
OL,9,Fcountry since the conflict with Iran
OL,10,Fbegan in late February, cautioning
OL,11,Fthat Iranian-backed militias could
OL,12,Fattempt to kidnap Americans. "Do not
OL,13,Ftravel to Iraq for any reason. Depart
OL,14,Fimmediately if you are there," the
OL,15,Fembassy said in its latest statement
OL,16,Fover the weekend.
OL,26,@tD@^OUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FThe Committee to Protect Journalists
OL,8,F(CPJ) said it is monitoring press
OL,9,Ffreedom violations related to the
OL,10,Fongoing military escalation between
OL,11,FIsrael, the US and Iran.
OL,13,FSince the war broke out on February
OL,14,F28, they say they have documented the
OL,15,Farrests of journalists, interference
OL,16,Fwith reporting, restrictions on the
OL,17,Fregion and damage caused by airstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FTheir statement came after three
OL,8,Fjournalists were killed in an Israeli
OL,9,Fairstrike in the south of Lebanon on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FHezbollah's al-Manar TV said its
OL,13,Flongtime correspondent Ali Shoeib was
OL,14,Fkilled in southern Lebanon. Israel's
OL,15,Fmilitary said it had targeted Shoeib,
OL,16,Faccusing him of being a Hezbollah
OL,17,Fintelligence operative, without
OL,18,Fproviding evidence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FA well-known Lebanese war
OL,8,Fcorrespondent, Shoeib, had covered
OL,9,Fsouthern Lebanon for al-Manar TV for
OL,10,Fnearly three decades.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Beirut-based pan-Arab Al-
OL,13,FMayadeen TV said reporter Fatima
OL,14,FFtouni was killed in the same
OL,15,Fairstrike in the southern district of
OL,16,FJezzine along with her brother
OL,17,FMohammed, a video journalist.
OL,19,FShe had just been on air with a live
OL,20,Freport before the strike.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775052666
OL,3,CUS journalist Shelly Kittleson
OL,4,Ckidnapped by 'Iran-backed militia' in
OL,5,CIraq
OL,7,FTop officials in Lebanon condemned the
OL,8,Fstrike, with President Joseph Aoun
OL,9,Fcalling it a "flagrant crime that
OL,10,Fviolates all laws and agreements that
OL,11,Fprotect journalists."
OL,13,FOn Thursday, CNN reported that Israeli
OL,14,Fsoldiers had detained and assaulted
OL,15,Fone of their crews in the West Bank,
OL,16,Fwhere journalists were documenting
OL,17,Fsettler violence.
OL,19,FThe CPJ said the incident constituted
OL,20,Fa "clear infringement on journalists'
OL,21,Fright to document and report."
OL,26,@qD@NOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
